description:
Recently a Bible has been promoted as the &quot;1599 Geneva Bible&quot; when, in fact, it is not. Unsuspecting Bible believers may be deceived into thinking it is safe to read and study from, but the facts in this book will point out many of the flaws of this &quot;Trojan Horse.&quot;


